imdb.plot outline: Paris Dylan hosts 'PARIS in LA' a live video streaming radio podcast talk show on iTunes, USTREAM, LiveStream, and TradioV networks. With sassy co-host Hollywood stylist Jen Rade, the show brings guests weekly to discuss stuff and things, but mostly stuff. Be sure to tune in for your weekly dose of funny!
